room_title: Escape room "Hijacked" by RISE Escape Rooms in Tickfaw
review: We did Hijacked tonight and it was so much fun! Very challenging and definitely tests your ability to work as a team. Cannot wait to go back and try another one!

room_title: Escape room "Hijacked" by RISE Escape Rooms in Tickfaw
review: We had a blast. First escape room experience. We picked the hijacked to try out. It was fun. Staff was fantastic. Will be going back to try the next level.

room_title: Escape room "Hijacked" by RISE Escape Rooms in Tickfaw
review: This place is awesome! My fiance and I did the Hijacked escape room. We loved everything about it! The staff was very friendly and helpful. It feels so real when you're trying to crack codes and solve puzzles to escape! Teamwork is key. I recommend this place for sure!

room_title: Escape room "Hijacked" by RISE Escape Rooms in Tickfaw
review: Our team of escapers decided to stop in Tickfaw about a month ago as a part of an escape room tour. Sincerely one of the best experiences we have had. I wont spoil any of the games but if you like escape rooms, you absolutely must stop here and play Hijacked. It is one of the best rooms I have ever played. The owners are super cool and truly know what they are doing!
